The overall dependence of J on α demonstrates a complex behaviour that is well described by an oscillating function consisting of four components2J(α)=D+C⋅ sin2α+L1⋅ cos4α+L2⋅ sin4α\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
